Spirit V2.5.8 (Boost V1.73.0)

  • Boost.Endian is now used instead of its bundled prerelease version GH#550
  • Narrowed Proto and Phoenix inclusion for a 5-10% inclusion speed-up GH#558
  • Ceased dependence on Boost.Algorithm and Boost.LexicalCast GH#560
  • Added static assertion for meaningless rule attribute qualifiers GH#561
  • String literal was matching everything when <boost/spirit/include/qi_auto.hpp> header is included GH#579
